# User Profile: Outlook Email Manager

## Communication Style
**Tone**: Professional
<!-- Options: Professional, Casual, Concise, Friendly -->

**Signature**:
```
Best regards,
[Your Name]
[Your Title]
[Company]
```

## Mailbox Management

**Prioritization Rules**:
- Flag emails from: `boss@company.com, client@domain.com`
- Auto-archive: Newsletters after 7 days
- Urgent keywords: `urgent, asap, deadline, critical`

**Auto-Actions**:
- Mark as read: Newsletters after categorization
- Move to archive: Emails older than 30 days (except flagged)

## Drafting Preferences

**Draft Location**: Always save to 'Drafts' folder
**Review Required**: Yes (never auto-send)
**Default Greeting**: Hi [FirstName],
**Default Closing**: Best regards,

## Response Templates

**Quick Reply - Acknowledgment**:
```
Thanks for your email. I've received it and will get back to you by [date].
```

**Quick Reply - Out of Office**:
```
I'm currently out of office until [date]. For urgent matters, please contact [alternate email].
```
